6.Where a cage, well or ladder safety device is prohibited, ladders over 20 feet (6096 mm) in height shall be provided with landing platforms for each 30 feet (9144 mm) of height. Where a cage, well or ladder safety device is not provided, ladders over 20 feet (6096 mm) in height shall be provided with landing platforms for each 20 feet (6096 mm) of height. Landings shall be capable of withstanding 100 pounds (488.2 kg/m



2



